    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先用饼图把结构搭出来：标题NETFLIX，两个区块分别是'Time spent looking for movie'90和'Time spent watching it'10。",
