      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，'Time spent looking for movie'后面是不是该加个s？movie要复数吧，因为找的不止一部。",
